    "## Add & Norm = Feed Forward + Layers Norm + Residual Connection \n",
    "\n",
    "![image.png](attachment:image.png)\n",
    "\n",
    "`LayerNorm(x + Sublayer(x))` - layer normalization apply to each SubLayer(x)\n"
   ]
